{"tid":2424557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 19歲正妹電莖損手遭刺死 兇手還把屍體照上傳群組「我就是想這樣做」","createTime":"2021-02-26T16:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T16:47:16.000Z","uid":17387,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"edcd6f77a611590be51514052a583f80504291d2","tid":2424557,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/vPDTd0gXgYM_kgLSaGQdg2sXVRM=/1800x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3PZ6UH63EBAEZOFCQUFSYNYOGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvPDTd0gXgYM_kgLSaGQdg2sXVRM%3D%2F1800x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3PZ6UH63EBAEZOFCQUFSYNYOGY.jpg&h=0972ea81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西電競圈發生出一件慘絕人寰的兇殺案件。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，年僅19歲的《決勝時刻Mobile》正妹電競選手Sol(Ingrid Oliveira Bueno da Silva)日前到同為《決勝時刻》的男選手Flashlight(Guilherme Alves Costa)家中打遊戲，卻沒想到Flashlight突然持刀將Sol刺殺，事後還將屍體照片傳上友人間的群組中，他原本打算自殺，但在友人勸說下，犯案約30分鐘後就向警方自首投案。<br />\n<br />\nFlashlight向警方表示自己是預謀犯案，認識Sol之後就開始計畫，且殺人當下神智清楚，被問到殺人動機，他僅回答「她擋到我的路」、「我就是想這麼做」，警方事後在他的筆記本中發現了犯案計畫。<br />\n<br />\nSol的命案震撼巴西電競圈，不少知名電競戰隊都在推特發文哀悼，當地女性受暴力傷害的社會事件頻傳，女性電競選手也時常受到騷擾，女性人身安全問題再度浮出檯面。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"beb29f27a6d68a45d1003928d3c848f6e6a82a0f","tid":2424557,"uid":59328,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"屍體相呢"},{"pid":"e71f6dda7d715b6d8d9359d44b675fe1ad4f51e5","tid":2424557,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"巴西連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd62d26c278f801cc7aa43d74fcd08ba8d7a038","tid":2424557,"uid":37136,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"玩隻垃圾電話驚